oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Morfological features and phenylpropanoid contents of natural and cultivated Rhodiola rosea roots in Finland
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Galambosi, B.
Galambosi, Zs.
Slacanin, I.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Crop husbandry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Root samples of Rhodiola rosea were collected from three places during June 2006 and the morphological and chemical features were compared to cultivated accessions.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Galambosi, B.; Galambosi, Zs. and Slacanin, I. (2007) Morfological features and phenylpropanoid contents of natural and cultivated Rhodiola rosea roots in Finland. In: NJF Report, Nordic Association of Agricultural Scientists, pp. 38-39.
